resources.string:
 1. Click “PLAY” button to start rolling the dices;
2. A dialogue pop up for you to choose your die number;
3. Click “OK” to submit your number;
4. A dialogue pop up to show you the results;
5. Click “CONTINUE” to play the next round;
6. Click” EXIT” to exit the game;
7. Click “STATS” to review the results history;
8. Click “HELP” to read the game instruction;
